  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women who underwent a clinically indicated cesarean delivery after the onset of labor
             or rupture of membranes

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cesarean delivery prior to the onset of labor or rupture of membranes

          -  emergent cesarean delivery

          -  general endotracheal anesthesia

          -  clinical chorioamnionitis

          -  HIV infection

          -  less than 16 years of age
